  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "underestimated the power of an external-to-the-person world Guarantor. (my worlds in my writing were solipsistic.) (well, no, not in \"Stigmata\". It looks more & more as if \"Stigmata\" is correct.)\n\nVia my writing I must have signaled YHWH, & he responded. He is indeed a world Generator, _which he must feed directly to our senses._ So we are in a cold-pac situation : \"Joint\" - info basis \"Stigmata\" - plural worlds manufactured \"Ubik\" - our situation & the entity which manufactures the worlds \"Maze",
      "matched_alias": "Buddhist",
      "term_id": "TERM_buddhist",
      "term_name": "Buddhist",
      "term_slug": "buddhist"
    },
    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 49 - 004\n(1004)\n\nWe (1) don't have a long enough present -- perceptual memory -- & (2) it needs to be seen speeded up. It is thinking, & and its thoughts are physical information. This may be Teilhard de Chardin's Omega Point. Or is it, as I long ago surmised, an invader & camouflaged in our reality? a Macro-organism!\n\nEverything hinges on the question of whether it creates reality or has invaded it. No; wrong. Consider Jn 1. It could be the wisdom-word entering its own creation &",
      "matched_alias": "Chardin",
      "term_id": "TERM_chardin",
      "term_name": "Chardin",
      "term_slug": "chardin"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n80\nNeeds Review\n80\n50 So I have no idea what I would have been ordered to do had I responded to the Xerox missive. Turn over the scientic data to them probably. All those pages + pages of diagrams + writing. (\"We are DNA memor coils who have recorded + stored experiential info, but there is a failure to play back.) Here is the crucial insight. I had re t corded + stored, but failed to play back when The trigger-signal was given; in fact I did worse th",
      "matched_alias": "Friday",
      "term_id": "TERM_friday",
      "term_name": "Friday",
      "term_slug": "friday"
    }
  ],
